{"tid":1669524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"根本選民登記冊禁制令係好事","createTime":"2019-10-22T15:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:57.000Z","uid":41458,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"34f89d8bf8375d3451b1e05412d7b43f92efb791","tid":1669524,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:07:35.000Z","msg":"今時今日, 雖然流水革命已經開始左4個月<br />\n但香港仍然有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好大部分既和理非同港豬</span></span>, 係各方面自由被嚴重打擊下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>妄想繼續苟且係僅餘既安逸</strong></span></span>, 繼續返工, 得閒就行下街當抗爭左<br />\n對香港被全面操控既選舉抱有一絲不切實際既期望<br />\n<br />\n而今次禁制令就係畀香港人知<br />\n我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔應該再對任何香港制度以內既方法有任何期望</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭同攬炒係香港唯一既出路</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e41d2f1b002c62960d973ff9a69427a68c0cbdd2","tid":1669524,"uid":143151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"事實上 佢哋唔會知嚟單新聞 亦唔覺得影響到佢"},{"pid":"d802b028b7657723e8bc4f644f0b4fe2f478ec17","tid":1669524,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c475813b81f91ddf768e17fd0949767afef820","tid":1669524,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"now區選情報Telegram Channel <a href=\"https://t.me/nowpolitics_dc2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnowpolitics_dc2019&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=19e365f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nowpolitics_dc2019</a>"},{"pid":"